	B&C Electronic Engineering










Electronic Design from Concept to completion
B&C Electronic Engineering, Inc. was founded in 1984 to make existing technologies and processes BETTER and more efficient than previous equipment. We also assist in developing new CUSTOM ideas from concept, prototype to production using the latest technology available.
Our engineers are committed to each project in order to bring your ideas to fruition. We accomplish this by listening to your concerns, understanding your solution, and combining your institutional knowledge with our expertise. 














